quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  40,21,Kya yeh log kabhi zameen mein chaley phiray nahin hain ke inhein un logon ka anjaam nazar aata jo insey pehle guzar chuke hain? Woh insey zyada taaqatwar thay aur insey zyada zabardast aasaar zameen mein chodh gaye hain. Magar Allah ne unke gunahon par unhein pakad liya aur unko Allah se bachane wala koi na tha
  40,22,Yeh unka anjaam is liye hua ke unke paas unke
  40,23,Humne Moosa ko
  40,24,"Firoun aur Haaman aur Qaroon ki taraf apni nishaniyon aur numaya sanad-e-maamoriyat ke saath bheja. Magar unhon ne kaha “ saahir(jaadugar) hai, kazzab(jhoota) hai”"
  40,25,Phir jab woh hamari taraf se haqq unke saamne ley aaya to unhon ne kaha “jo log imaan laa kar iske saath shamil huey hain in sabke ladkon ko qatal karo aur ladkiyon ko jeeta (zinda) chodh do”. Magar kaafiron ki chaal akarat (vain) hi gayi
  40,26,"Ek roz Firoun ne apne darbariyon se kaha “chodo mujhey main is Moosa ko qatal kiye deta hoon, aur pukar dekhe yeh apne Rubb ko.Mujhey andesha hai ke yeh tumhara deen badal daalega, ya mulk mein fasaad barpa karega”"
  40,27,Moosa ne kaha “maine to har us mutakabbir (ghamandi) ke muqable mein jo yaum ul hisaab par imaan nahin rakhta apne Rubb aur tumhare Rubb ki panaah ley li hai”